title: The Spotify Before Spotify... Ended in Tragedy

author: Nostalgia Nerd
description:
Can you believe it's been over 4 years since we last went Thrifting? The British Charity Shops and Car Boot Sales are crying out for some love. Thankfully and rightfully, I decided it was time to get back on the #thriftwagon and go check out some technology bargains, Thrifting UK Style. Because YouTube needs more of this kinda thing! #thrift #thrifthaul 

We also take a look at Sheringham's 1940s Weekend, and a huge, and terrifying bookshop... which was interesting.
